The paper discusses the effectiveness of deep learning methods in reinforcement learning, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The focus on value-based learning and policy-based learning suggests that the paper may also be relevant to robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY).
